name: ExportOptionsWebOptimizedSVG

properties.name: fontType
properties.description: The type of font that should be included in the exported file.

properties.name: coordinatePrecision
properties.description: Decimal precision for element coordinate values.

properties.name: cssProperties
properties.description: How should the CSS properties of the document be included in the document.

properties.name: svgId
properties.description: How object names (IDs) are generated in exported SVG.

properties.name: svgMinify
properties.description: Reduces the size of the svg.

properties.name: rasterImageLocation
properties.description: Should the raster images in the exported file be included.

properties.name: saveMultipleArtboards
properties.description: All the artboards or range of the artboards will be saved.

properties.name: artboardRange
properties.description: If SaveMultipleArtboards is true,this will be considered for multi-asset extraction which specifies artboard range.Empty string will extracts all the artboards.Default is empty string.

description: Options which may be supplied when exporting a document as a Web optimized SVG file.
